---
<Layout title={title} description={description} canonical={canonical}>
  <Fragment slot="head-scripts">
    {schemaJsons.map((schema) => (<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)} />))}
  </Fragment>

  <section class="ph-hero">
    <div class="ph-wrap">
      <p class="ph-eyebrow">Placeholder · Content Coming Soon</p>
      <h1>Outdoor Refrigerator Repair in Los Angeles</h1>
      <p class="ph-intro">Outdoor kitchens in Malibu, Bel Air, Hidden Hills, and Newport Coast specify weather-rated refrigeration — Sub-Zero, Viking, U-Line, Perlick. These aren’t indoor refrigerators in stainless skins; they’re sealed UL-listed outdoor units engineered for ambient swings, salt air (coastal), and patio installation. We service compressor circuits, evaporator fans, door seals, and control boards across all four major brands.</p>
      <div class="ph-ctas">
        <a href="tel:+14243250520" class="ph-btn">Call (424) 325-0520</a>
        <a href="/contact/" class="ph-btn ph-btn-ghost">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="ph-faq">
    <div class="ph-wrap">
      <h2>Frequently Asked</h2>
      {faqs.map(f => (<details class="ph-detail"><summary>{f.q}</summary><p>{f.a}</p></details>))}
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .ph-wrap { max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }
  .ph-hero { background: #0a0a0a; color: #fff; padding: 64px 0; }
  .ph-eyebrow { color: #C8102E; font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.14em; margin: 0 0 14px; }
  .ph-hero h1 { font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.2vw, 2.4rem); font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 16px; line-height: 1.2; }
  .ph-intro { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); font-size: 1.05rem; margin: 0 0 28px; line-height: 1.65; }
  .ph-ctas { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .ph-btn { display: inline-block; background: #C8102E; color: #fff; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .ph-btn-ghost { background: transparent; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4); }
  .ph-faq { padding: 56px 0; background: #f5f5f5; }
  .ph-faq h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 0 0 20px; color: #0a0a0a; }
  .ph-detail { background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e2e2e2; padding: 14px 18px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .ph-detail summary { font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; color: #0a0a0a; }
  .ph-detail p { margin: 10px 0 0; color: #444; line-height: 1.6; }
</style>
